00:28:10.680 --> 00:28:13.440
[Guest 2]: having the institutions to push it through.

00:28:13.440 --> 00:28:18.080
[Amit Varma]: I mean, interestingly, like a few episodes ago, I spoke to Karthik Shashidhar on futures

00:28:18.080 --> 00:28:22.000
[Amit Varma]: markets in agriculture, which either they are not allowed to trade in future markets

