00:28:40.040 --> 00:28:44.440
[Guest 2]: I mean, any market needs its, you know, there, I mean, obviously, every market needs speculators

00:28:44.440 --> 00:28:49.600
[Guest 2]: for it to operate efficiently, but you need the genuine guys as well.

