00:29:09.280 --> 00:29:10.280
[Amit Varma]: anything.

00:29:10.280 --> 00:29:11.280
[Amit Varma]: Sure.

00:29:11.280 --> 00:29:12.280
[Amit Varma]: Unseen effect number one is moral hazard.

00:29:12.280 --> 00:29:18.520
