00:29:18.520 --> 00:29:19.520
[Amit Varma]: pay.

00:29:19.520 --> 00:29:22.760
[Amit Varma]: So essentially, and because it continues every election cycle, it's just…

00:29:22.760 --> 00:29:25.440
[Guest 1]: It destroys the credit discipline of the market.

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:30.880
[Amit Varma]: Number two, it is essentially a redistribution of wealth from the people at large to farmers.

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:34.680
[Amit Varma]: And it's a redistribution, not just directly, but in a number of different ways.

00:29:34.680 --> 00:29:39.080
