00:29:47.340 --> 00:29:51.400
[Amit Varma]: And if they borrow at a higher rate, that cost is then passed on to consumers.

00:29:51.400 --> 00:29:53.520
[Amit Varma]: It's just that it's not very clearly measurable.

00:29:53.520 --> 00:29:54.520
[Amit Varma]: It's not measurable.

00:29:54.520 --> 00:29:55.520
[Amit Varma]: It's an unseen effect.

00:29:55.520 --> 00:29:59.800
