00:30:00.800 --> 00:30:02.760
[Amit Varma]: So it has an impact all the way down the line.

00:30:02.760 --> 00:30:06.180
[Amit Varma]: In a sense, it's a negative sum game, you could say.

00:30:06.180 --> 00:30:08.100
[Amit Varma]: These are the two main unseen effects.

